                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Varius <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> Verecundus <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>vet</abbr><ex>eranus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XV <expan><abbr>Apoll</abbr><ex>inaris</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>dom</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> Lepido Regio <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> CVIII et Varia <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>lib</abbr><ex>erta</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>Margale <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> LXXX <lb n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">hic siti</supplied> sunt <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Fragment einer Grabstele, oben und unten abgebrochen. Schriftfeld von Pilastern mit Weinranken gerahmt. Gefunden in sekundärer Verwendung als Abdeckplatte einer spätantiken Wasserleitung. Z. 2: VA-, ND-Ligaturen; V klein in C eingeschrieben; Z. 5: VA-, IB-Ligaturen. (B): Beutler 2014/15: Z. 5: überflüssiger Zeilenfall Varia / L(uci).</p>
            </div>
